snippet.title: LIBBY'S® Famous Pumpkin Pie
snippet.description: This is the traditional holiday pumpkin pie. This classic recipe has been on LIBBY'S® Pumpkin labels since 1950. This pie is easy to prepare and even easier to enjoy. Just mix, pour, bake for a delicious homemade tradition.

snippet.title: Mini Pumpkin Cranberry Breads
snippet.description: Mini Pumpkin Cranberry Breads are perfect for snacking and easy to make, too. These colorful mini-breads are excellent for holiday gift giving.

snippet.title: Island Cookies
snippet.description: The coconut and nut combination give these Island Cookies a tropical flavor! Great for picnics and entertaining, too.
